Share this on WhatsAppA lawmaker in the Delta State House of Assembly, Kenneth Ogba, was declared dead on Sunday. The legislator represented Isoko South Local Government Area in the House before his death.
Details of the death are still scanty. However, a notice was issued on Sunday: “Sad One… We just lost Delta House of Assembly member Representing Isoko South LGA, Kenneth Ogba now.
“This is sad and painful
“May his soul RIP.”
